name: What's in a letter.
description:
What's in a Letter; Q, Fragments,
 
Abstract bricolage constructed from photographs of inked slides and other images projected from an analogue and digital projectors, and video of typewriting. Digitally overlapped and animated with scanned pages and screenshots. Audio from the typewriting video and a rain shower 

| This piece was created for The Orphanage's fifth Non-Fungible Thunderdome Art Contest. | 00:39 | 1920x1080 | Audio recorded/generated by artist |
